    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Nos <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/90 #people/298"
                            >Guaimarius</persName> divina providentia Langobardorum gentis <rs
                            key="#Princeps">princeps</rs> concedimus vobis omnibus <rs key="#Monks"
                            >monachis</rs> ex monasterio <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/84"
                            key="#Monasteries"> Sancti Benedicti</orgName> qui situ(m) est in
                            <placeName ref="#places/109"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Public_exactions #Datium #Privileges #Exemption"
                            >Monte castro Casino</placeName>, ut amodo et deinceps licentiam et
                        potestatem abeatis veniendi in civitatem nostram <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/84">Salernitanam</placeName> et vendendi et emendi ea quę
                        nobis necessaria sunt sine omni requisitione vel contrarietate nostre rei
                        publicę, et non detis exinde <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Public_exactions #Datium #Exemption">plateaticum
                            vel aliquam dationem in partibus nostrę rei publice</rs> vel cuicumque
                        homini et nec a nostris comitibus, castaldeis vel a quibuscumque hominibus
                        abeatis inde aliqua contrarietate, sed amodo et deinceps per hunc nostrum
                        roboreum scriptum firmum stabilemque permaneat. Quod scribere precepimus
                            <persName key="#Writer #Other_clerics" ref="#people/4156"
                            >Urso</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clerico</rs>
                        <rs key="#Writer">scriba</rs> nostri Palatii intus suprascripto monasterio,
                        de mense Iulio, indictione secunda.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
